INTRODUCTION
============

This module provides access to the Flixster api.


INSTALLATION
============

   1 perl Makefile.PL
   2 make
   3 make test
   4 make install # as superuser


DEPENDENCIES
============

Class::Accessor
Cache::FileCache
DateTime::Duration
DateTime::Incomplete
File::Spec::Functions
HTML::Entities
JSON
LWP::UserAgent
Math::Currency
URI


